noria:TroubleTicket002 noria:troubleTicketPartyIntervention foaf:Agent008 .
noria:TroubleTicket003 noria:troubleTicketPartyIntervention foaf:Agent004 .

# Operation Plan to Anomaly Pattern
noria:OperationPlan001 seas:solves folio:FailureMode . # General relation
noria:OperationPlan001 seas:solves noria:AnomalyPattern001 .
noria:OperationPlan002 seas:solves noria:AnomalyPattern002 .
noria:OperationPlan003 seas:solves noria:AnomalyPattern003 .

# Anomaly Pattern to Event Records (as examples)
